<p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 250, 239);">在如今浮躁的社会，我不知道还有多少人记住了远去的</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 250, 239); font-family: Calibri; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">81192</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 250, 239);">，但我相信，依旧有人，有很多人，怀着悲痛祭奠我们的海空卫士——王伟，祭奠我们的那架</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 250, 239); font-family: Calibri; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">81192</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 250, 239);">！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 250, 239);"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEJUyoz1WWR90UPtZAjfYibicYYHc2nlQchCP3gPia7ia2gE9cy414hO1X96t7Q71JWElnlDiaicjLfjKWJA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="330" height="180" style="width: 330px; height: 180px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 250, 239); text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">2001年1月20日小布什就任美国第43届总统。他上台后对中国的外交政策做了一定的调整。在国际方面，小布什上台刚两个月，美俄之间就爆发了冷战结束以来最大规模的驱逐对方外交官的大战。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 250, 239); text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">美俄两国关系日趋紧张。在对华政策方面，小布什放弃了克林顿时期关于建立中美&quot;战略合作伙伴&quot;关系的表述，反而在竞选过程中将中美关系定位为&quot;战略竞争对手&quot;。公开表示克林顿政府对华政策太软弱，应当增加强硬的成分。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 250, 239); text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">中国政府对中美关系非常重视。2001年3月19日，中国政府派钱其琛副总理访美，旨在沟通信息，增进彼此之间的信任。访问取得了圆满成功。美方放弃了&quot;战略竞争对手&quot;这样咄咄逼人的提法，布什总统同时还表示&quot;特别渴望到中国访问&quot;。中美之间的紧张气氛缓解。</span></p><p><br/></p>